## Usage

```svelte
<script>
  import { Accordion, AccordionGroup } from 'renderless-svelte';
</script>

<AccordionGroup>
  <Accordion>...</Accordion>
  <Accordion>...</Accordion>
  <Accordion>...</Accordion>
