## Properties

| Name        | Type   | Default        | Description                                        |
| ----------- | ------ | -------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| contextName | string | "rs-accordion" | Changes the name of the context for the ContextAPI |

<HintBlock title="Changing the contextName">
